  <name>Tarball Installer</name>
  <summary>Install tarballs as native applications</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A modern, user-friendly application for installing software from tarball archives.
      Converts downloaded .tar.gz, .tar.bz2, and .tar.xz files into properly integrated
      desktop applications with menu entries and proper system integration.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Simple graphical interface for tarball installation</li>
      <li>Automatic desktop entry creation</li>
      <li>User or system-wide installation options</li>
      <li>Package analysis and preview</li>
      <li>Installation logging</li>
      <li>Modern GNOME-inspired interface</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
